      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved specimen, currently maintained in showroom condition. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector, exhibiting flawless aesthetic integrity and peak mechanical performance. Every detail has been rigorously scrutinized to ensure it meets our most exacting standards for excellence. For those who demand nothing less than the superlative, this offering stands as a testament to automotive perfection.",
      "price": 47800.0,
